<p class="">In view of the threatening situation in the Near and Middle East and the importance of our communications in the Mediterranean area, does the right hon. Gentleman hope to speed up these negotiations and obtain a settlement as soon as possible?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
