<p class="">With very great respect, and bowing humbly to your decision on the point of order, may I be permitted to submit to you that there is a certain strategic connection between the two ideas which comes outside the ordinary principles of order? [HON. MEMBERS: "Order."] Mr. Speaker is the judge of order, and if he calls me to order, I will sit down. Therefore, may I have an answer on this point?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
